title: Episode 7 of 7 | Hurley Presents "Twelve": A New Series From John John Florence
description:
The competitive year is over, but in the final episode of “Twelve,” it’s clear that John John Florence is just getting started.

See more at http://hurley.com/jjf

EPISODE SUMMARY
Episode 7 of “Twelve” showcases the end of John John’s competitive season and highlights how he’s been spending his down time before the start of the 2017 WSL Tour. 

--

CREDITS
Directed by: Bill Ballard and Parallel Sea Productions
Filmed by: Erik Knutson
Creative Direction and Post Production: Instrument (http://www.instrument.com/)

--

MUSIC 
00:00 Alexander “Truth”
02:43 Drakkar Nowhere “Higher Now”
06:51 Red Fang “Wires”
10:10 Olomana “Ku'u Home O Kahala’u”
